<div id="content" class="content wikipage" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p id="l1">
On a <a title="Web Press" href="Web_Press">web press</a>, a roller located on a <a title="Roll Stand" href="Roll_Stand">roll stand</a> between the roll and the first <a title="Dancer Roller" href="Dancer_Roller">dancer roller</a>, used during paper infeed to compensate for variations in paper roll conditions. Also called a <a title="Cocking Roller" href="Cocking_Roller">cocking roller</a>. 
</p>
